Enkaji e Solomon e nkitoo


1  Ilarin tomon ookuni apa etesheta Solomon enkaji enye, neidip ninye enchetata enkaji pooki.


2  Etesheta ninye enkaji e ntim e Lebanon; ore enkadoro enye naa ntemat enkaina iip nabo ore endapasho naa ntemat e nkaina onom, ore enkadoro eilep naa ntemat e nkaina tomoni uni, neteshetaki apa too lkererin ooiriamari okuni too ng'apeta o ltarakuai, o rishinani oltarakuai te shumata ing'apeta. 
3  Neimulumuli apa shumata lelo gilat te lelo tarakua ootipikaki shumata nena ng'apeta artam oimiet, etii ake iltarakua tomon o imiet olkereri obo. 
4  Netii apa irubat oo lusien olkereri ake obo, netii apa ilusien aaipira too nkaloli pokira, katitin uni. 
5  Ore njing'eta pooki oo nkajijik o lusien naa kerisioro too nchot pooki. Ore ake elusie neipirakinore elusie katitin uni eiriamari maare.


6  Neitobir ninye enkaji nalala oo ng'apeta; ore enkadoro enye naa ntemat onom e nkaina, ore endapasho enye naa ntemat tomoni uni e nkaina. Netii apa olodungoro dukuya enye oitobiruno too ng'apeta, netii enkitushuret dukuya ninye.


7  Neitobir ninye enkaji nalala o lorika le nkitoo teine nedung'ie ninye enkiguana, aa taa enkaji e nkiguana, neitobiri too ltarakua ebaiki oltiren o metabaiki shumata enye.


8   Ore enkaji enye makewan naa ninye, etonie, tiae dung'oroto te siadi ina aji nalala, naa neijia ake eikunuaki olchetei. Enyaaka ake sii Solomon aitobiru enkaji natiu anaa ena aji nalala tenkaraki entito e Farao apa nayama.


9  Eitobiruaki kuna pooki too soito oogol enkinyiang'a, ootaguetaki te risioroto naba anaa enairirikino, neiriri te musumeno, oriong o atua, ebaiki olkitamanyunoto o metabaiki shumata. Ore ebaiki endung'oroto e nkaji o Laitoriani o metabaiki endung'oroto kitok. 
10  Ore apa olkitamanyunoto naa oloo soito oogol enkinyiang'a, isoito sapuki oleng, isoito loo ntemat isiet anaa ntemat tomon enkaina. 
11  Ore shumata naa isoito oogol enkinyiang'a, ooguetuno anaa enairirikino, tenebo iltarakua. 
12  Ore apa ina dung'oroto kitok neeta ilkererin okuni too soito oogueta oomanita o lkereri loo loom to ltarakuai, neeta sii nena ina dung'oroto e atua e nkaji o Laitoriani, o lodung'oro ojing'ieki enkaji.

Esiaai e Huram


13  Neirriwaa olaiguanani Solomon meyauni Huram aaitung'uaa Turo. 
14  Olayioni apa ninye le nkoliai o losho le Naftali, ore menye naa oltung'ani le Turo, olaitobirani lo suyai; naa ngen apa ninye oleng, neeta engeno nagut sapuk o ening'unoto o enkarriyiano te nkitobirata e pooki siaai o suyai. Nelotu ninye enetii olaiguanani Solomon, neas esiaai enye pooki.

