15  Etipika apa ninye ing'apeta are o suyai. Ntemat tomon oisiet enkadoro e ng'ape nabo, naa enkopito ntemat tomon oare enkaina naaman ake eng'ape nabo negum nchumat enye. Ore apa enkirrushai enye naa ilkimojik oong'uan neijia apa eikununo ing'apeta pokira are. 
16  Neitoki sii aitobir ntokitin e shumata naaikununo anaa nkopiyiani enkitoo, to suyai otosholaki, pee epiki shumata e nena ng'apeta; ore apa enkadoro entoki nabo naa ntemat imiet e nkaina. 
17  Neitoki aitobiru ntokitin are naashetuno anaa ilmarisiani to lpisiai, nepik shumata nena ng'apeta, netii ake ina toki nashetuno anaa olmarisian shumata nabo ng'ape netii enkae shumata enkae ng'ape. 
18  Neitoki ake sii aitobiru ilgululu oopurupurana oonyaanyukie kukumanka ilkererin oare pee eitoip nena lukuny oo ng'apeta. 
19  Ore apa nena kikompeni naatii ilukuny e nena ng'apeta neitobiruaki anaa ntapuka, naa ntemat ong'uan e nkaina. 
20  Netii apa nena kikompeni ilukuny e nena ng'apeta are, o shumata ina natii embata ena ripata olmarisian, netii apa ilgululu iip are, emanaa too lkererin oare, naa neija eikununo enkae toki te nchumata enkae ng'ape. 
21  Neitasheyie ninye nena ng'apeta ntaloishin pokira are e wueji nejing'ieki enkaji e Nkai; nepik ninye eng'ape enkalo e kopikop nejo enkarna eine Yakini; neitoki, apik eng'ape enkalo e moikuape nejo enkarna enye Boas. 
22  Ore too nchumat oo ng'apeta netii ntokitin naaitobiruaki anaa ntapuka sidain. Neaku eidipe apa esiaai oo ng'apeta.

