40  Eitobira apa sii Hiram imotioo, o nchempei naata ilala, o ngirran. Neaku eidipa apa Hiram esiaai pooki nataasaka Solomon tialo ina aji Olaitoriani: 
41  nena ng'apeta pokira are, o lelo bakulini pokira oare apa otii nchumat e nena ng'apeta, o nena sosin pokira are naaimulumul ilbakulini ootii nchumat oo ng'apeta. 
42  O lelo gululu iip ong'uan le nena sosin pokira are, ilkererin oare loo lgululu ake te sos nabo, pee eimulumul lelo bakulini oare loo nchumat oo ng'apeta; 
43  o nena kitasheta tomon o lelo motioo tomon ootii shumata nkitasheta tomon, 
44  oilo moti obo, o lelo oing'ok tomon oare ootii abori ilo moti.


45  Ore nena motioo, o nena kurteta, o ngirran, ore kuna masaa pooki naatii atua enkaji o Laitoriani, apa naaitobiraka Hiram olaiguanani Solomon, naa ino suyai otisikaki. 
46  Ore teina kisiajata e Yordan neiturraa olaiguanani ninche teina kop e nterit natii erishata e Sukot o Seretan. 
47  Neing'ua Solomon nena masaa pooki eitu etemi aaineneng enkaraki naa eikumok apa oleng. Ore enkiroishi o suyai neitu apa eyiolouni.


48   Neaku eitobira apa Solomon ntokitin pooki naatii atua enkaji o Laitoriani: ilo perere lo lasar le sahabu, ina misa e sahabu tenkaraki emukate naitisinyaki 
49   o nkitasheta oo ltaai e sahabu nasila, imiet te nkalo e kopikop o imiet te nkalo e moikuape, eitu ebaiki ilo gilata liatua; o ntapuka, o ltaai, o ntokitin naarieki iltaai e sahabu: 
50  o nkikompeni o nkalema o ngirran, o ntokitin e nkorropil, o ngirran e nkima, e sahabu, tenkaraki nena kikeneta e kutukaji e atua ilo gilata liatua, ine wueji nesinya aisul, o nena kikeneta olgos le nkaji e Nkai.


51   Neaku ina siaai pooki apa etaasa olaiguanani Solomon neidipayu ina aji o Laitoriani. Neitoki Solomon ayau nena tokitin apa naaitisinya Daudi papaai lenye, ina osholai, oina sahabu o nena masaa, neshum ninche te wueji neshumishoreki tiatua enkaji Olaitoriani.

